Argentina, Bolivia, Colombia, Ecuador, Peru, Brazil, Uruguay, Venezuela, Chile, Guyana, Surinam and Paraguay are members of the UNASUR, although the latter country is currently excluded.
Peru has the presidency at the time of the regional block.
